Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.34,0:25:42.25,NoteVertical,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\pos(1008,132)}月火DaYo！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.30,0:25:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,两个人合在一起就是Fire Sisters！
